Custom vim settings and plugins

Install:
    -- Link repo to filesystem --
    ln -s vimrc ~/.vimrc
    ln -s . ~/.vim

    -- Install Vundle --
    git clone https://github.com/gmarik/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

    -- Install all plugins --
    :PluginInstall (inside of vim)

    -- Install YCM autocomplete (https://github.com/Valloric/YouCompleteMe) --
    cd ~/.vim/bundle/YouCompleteME
    ./install.sh (--clang-completer for C languages support)

Requires:
    - vim compiled with python 2
    - git is installed
    - (optionl) cmake for YCM C lanuage support
    - (optional) silversearcher-ag for speady ctrlp
